item.title: CVE-2022-46774|2024-08-03T14:39:38.725Z -- ibm -- manage%20application
item.description: IBM Manage Application 8.8.0 and 8.9.0 in the IBM Maximo Application Suite is vulnerable to incorrect default permissions which could give access to a user to actions that they should not have access to. IBM X-Force ID: 242953.
